{
  "stem": "9601.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It'll be very nice for you if they ask you who your father is, you say Joseph Stalin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, up till today, there was so much laughing-- you know, not by the natives, by the soldiers, by the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They thought it was the funniest thing on earth-- never forget it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when I became aware that something was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After that, they began to-- I became aware about Hitler and Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I really did not-- I only heard the talks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I did not understand what they implied.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I should have asked, but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't know who to ask.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think I did a wise thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't ask my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would have probably got a spanking for asking stupid questions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About a month.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the war started, the Germans invaded Russia-- part of Russia-- where we lived in June of what, 21?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "June 21.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "July-- in July of 1941, we were in trouble.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I understood either way if there were German soldiers coming by-- because our village was close to the highway.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The highway was from Lvov to Kiev-- was one-- one big stretch on like a freeway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't a freeway, because who could use a freeway?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the Russians built a two-lane road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They established one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was paved-- you know, blacktop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Before then, the road was made out of stones, you know, those round stones like, I don't know, must have been artificially made, but they were-- when you rode in a horse and wagon, wagon goes-- shook all the way.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you picked up every stone that the wheel went on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, the Russians built a beautiful asphalt, like, you know, blacktop highway from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
